Sentencas: In this study, BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-alpha (BCEr10) powders were synthesized by the microemulsion method using anhydrous alcohol and PEG as the cosurfactant and surfactant, respectively.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-alpha-20 wt%NaCl-KCl (BCErl O-NaCl-KCl) composite was also synthesized by heating the BCEr10 with binary NaCl-KCl.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The physical chemistry changes in crystal phase formation and the microstructure of BCEr10 were determined by thermal gravimetry analysis-differential scanning calorimetry (TGA-DSC) and transmission electron microscopy (TEM).
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The BCEr10 and BCEr10-NaCl-KCl were characterized by XRD and SEM.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results revealed that the dense BCEr10-NaCl-KCl composite electrolyte was formed at a low temperature of 800 degrees C.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity was calculated from the AC impedance result.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The log sigma similar to log (pO(2)) plot result indicated that the composite is almost a pure ionic conductor.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Finally, the optimum performance of BCEr10-NaCl-KCl was obtained with a highest power density of 413 mW. cm(-2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: BaCe0.9Er0.1O3-α-NaCl-KCl Composite As Electrolyte for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
